      "text": "When Aang visited the Spirit World seeking the help of Tui and La to save the Northern Water Tribe, he disturbed a baboon spirit's meditation. A firefly passed by and the spirit suggested that Aang follow it, as it might lead him to what he was looking for. It led Aang to Avatar Roku, who told him about the spirit, Koh."
    },
    {
